it's not free either.

291
00:16:01,799 --> 00:16:02,799
Starting today,

292
00:16:03,559 --> 00:16:04,799
you have to work to pay it off.

293
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,600
What?

294
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,000
Not willing?

295
00:16:11,039 --> 00:16:12,119
I didn't even say anything.

296
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,600
How do you know what I'm thinking?

297
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,960
I feel like I've entered a fairytale world.

298
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,120
Where do I sleep?

299
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,640
You'll sleep here tonight.

300
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,800
Seems like there are still
plenty of mosquitos here.

301
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,440
I got bitten like this last night.

302
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,559
Could you really bear

303
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:52,000
to let me feed the mosquitoes again?

304
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:54,040
There's a mosquito
coil, I'll light one for you.

305
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,879
Your mattress is way too hard.

306
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,120
I just remembered,

307
00:17:00,279 --> 00:17:00,960
from the last time filming an action scene,

308
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,680
the back injury I got hasn't healed yet.

309
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,519
I... it hurts so much.

310
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,079
Well,

311
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,600
I'll go ask Grandma instead.

312
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:18,119
What exactly do you want?

313
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,440
I see...

314
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:24,119
isn't there a bed over there?

315
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,480
That's my bed.

316
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:30,759
That's fine.

317
00:17:31,146 --> 00:17:32,335
I'll reluctantly squeeze in with you.

318
00:17:32,359 --> 00:17:33,359
I don't mind.

319
00:17:35,039 --> 00:17:36,039
What "squeeze in"?

320
00:17:37,559 --> 00:17:39,119
Then how else are we supposed to sleep?

321
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,960
I just want to sleep

322
00:17:40,119 --> 00:17:41,279
in a bed with a mosquito net.

323
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,680
Tonight, you

324
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,920
either sleep here

325
00:17:48,799 --> 00:17:49,799
or get out.

326
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,720
Alright, alright, alright.

327
00:17:54,759 --> 00:17:55,759
I'll sleep here.

328
00:17:56,559 --> 00:17:58,159
Might as well let them bite me to death.

329
00:17:59,119 --> 00:18:00,119
My back

330
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,400
is so itchy.

331
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,440
My back

332
00:18:02,799 --> 00:18:03,799
is so itchy!

333
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:04,920
My back

334
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,000
is so itchy.

335
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,000
Don't move.

336
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:51,559
Sleep a little longer.

337
00:18:52,279 --> 00:18:53,279
You...

338
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,880
You...

339
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,160
"You" what?

340
00:18:57,359 --> 00:18:57,920
When did you

341
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:58,920
get into my bed?

342
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,080
What are you so nervous about?

343
00:19:02,519 --> 00:19:03,519
Just sleepwalking.

344
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,160
Sleepwalking?

345
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,880
Do you think I'd believe that?

346
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:08,720
There have been times before

347
00:19:08,721 --> 00:19:09,839
when this happened.

348
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:11,479
Even I don't remember myself

349
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,480
what occurred.

350
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,920
But I really didn't do it on purpose.

351
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:18,880
Really?

352
00:19:20,559 --> 00:19:21,559
Really.

353
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,480
Is that really necessary?

354
00:19:33,039 --> 00:19:34,799
It's just a normal
physiological phenomenon.

355
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,240
If you still want to keep living here,

356
00:19:41,599 --> 00:19:43,119
you must agree to three rules with me.

357
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,920
Starting tonight,

358
00:19:45,519 --> 00:19:46,575
if you can't control yourself

359
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:47,719
and climb into my bed again,

360
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,000
you get out.

361
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,000
But I really can't control it!

362
00:20:02,079 --> 00:20:03,480
You have this kind of fetish?

363
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,038
I'm telling you, if you can't control it,

364
00:20:05,039 --> 00:20:06,239
then tie yourself up to sleep.

365
00:20:08,279 --> 00:20:09,599
Will you be the one to tie me up?

366
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,000
Yes.

367
00:20:11,039 --> 00:20:12,200
And will you tie me up well?

368
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
You'll know once you try.

369
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:18,839
Make me breakfast.

370
00:20:28,559 --> 00:20:29,559
Sure enough, holding onto my "medicine"

371
00:20:29,559 --> 00:20:30,559
lets me sleep soundly.
